  "body": "Currently, all initial validators are set to PENDING_ACTIVE during `on_startup()`, this means the 16384 validators will get slowly trickle in instead of all at once. Not sure if this is correctly intended.\r\nGiven `MIN_VALIDATOR_SET_CHANGE_INTERVAL` is set to ~3%, best case scenario is all validators become ACTIVE after 36 hours",
